articles.author: Suzanne O'Halloran
articles.title: Trump's win gives US stocks best week of the year - Fox Business
articles.description: A Trump victory sent stock investors into beast buying mode, which was broad in nature with most sectors seeing big gains, minus the more defensive areas.
articles.content:
